mber  –  march  his imperial majesty the emperor and autocrat of all the russias  march  –  july  nicholas alexandrovich romanov since  saint nicholas the passion bearer nicholas iis full title as emperor as set forth in article  of the  constitution was by the grace of god we nicholas emperor and autocrat of all the russias of moscow kiev vladimir novgorod tsar of kazan tsar of astrakhan tsar of poland tsar of siberia tsar of tauric chersonesus lord of pskov and grand prince of smolensk lithuania volhynia podolia and finland prince of estonia livonia courland and semigalia samogitia bielostok karelia tver yugor perm vyatka bogar and others sovereign and grand prince of nizhni novgorod chernigov ryazan polotsk rostov jaroslavl beloozero udoria obdoria kondia vitebsk mstislav and ruler of all the severian country sovereign and lord of iveria kartalinia the kabardian lands and armenian province hereditary sovereign and possessor of the circassian and mountain princes and of others sovereign of turkestan heir of norway duke of schleswigholstein stormarn dithmarschen and oldenburg and so forth and so forth and so forth honoursedit emperor nicholas ii land in a  map of the russian empire back then it was believed that what is now severnaya zemlya was a single landmass emperor nicholas ii land russian земля императора николая ii zemlya imperatora nikolaya ii was discovered in  by the arctic ocean hydrographic expedition led by boris vilkitsky on behalf of the russian hydrographic service still incompletely surveyed the new territory was officially named in the emperors honour by order of the secretary of the imperial navy in  the archipelago was renamed severnaya zemlya in  by the presidium of the central executive committee of the soviet union domestic nicholas ii in the uniform of chevalier guard regiment  after his coronation nicholas ii leaves dormition cathedral the chevalier guard lieutenant marching in front to the tsars right is carl gustaf mannerheim later president of finland he was grand master of the following orders order of st andrew order of st alexander nevsky order of the white eagle order of st anne order of st stanislaus st class order of st vladimir th class order of saint george th class king chulalongkorn of siam with nicholas ii in saint petersburg during the kings visit to europe in  foreign  mecklenburgstrelitz grand cross of the house order of the wendish crown  january   netherlands knight grand cross of the order of the netherlands lion  march   oldenburg grand cross of the house and merit order of peter frederick louis  april   japan order of the rising sun grand cordon with paulownia flowers  september   baden grand cross of the house order of loyalty  may   spain order of the golden fleece  may   portugal knight grand cross of the order of christ  may   saxeweimareisenach knight of the house order of the white falcon  may   sweden knight of the royal order of the seraphim  may   grand duchy of hesse grand cross of the grand ducal ludwig order  may   kingdom of bavaria knight of the order of saint hubert  may   belgium grand cordon of the order of leopold  may   bulgaria grand cross of the order of st alexander  may   greece grand cross of the order of the redeemer  may   denmark knight of the order of the elephant  may   france grand cross of the legion of honour  may   holy see grand cross of the order of the holy sepulchre jerusalem patriarchate  may   hungary grand cross of the order of saint stephen of hungary  may   kingdom of italy order of the most holy annunciation  may   kingdom of italy knight grand cross of the order of saints maurice and lazarus  may   kingdom of italy knight grand cross of the order of the crown of italy  may   prussia order of the black eagle  may   romania grand cross with collar of the order of the star of romania  may   württemberg grand cross of the order of the crown  may   ottoman empire grand cross of the order of osmanieh  july   persia portrait of the shah of per