aya zemlya in  by the presidium of the central executive committee of the soviet union domestic nicholas ii in the uniform of chevalier guard regiment  after his coronation nicholas ii leaves dormition cathedral the chevalier guard lieutenant marching in front to the tsars right is carl gustaf mannerheim later president of finland he was grand master of the following orders order of st andrew order of st alexander nevsky order of the white eagle order of st anne order of st stanislaus st class order of st vladimir th class order of saint george th class king chulalongkorn of siam with nicholas ii in saint petersburg during the kings visit to europe in  foreign  mecklenburgstrelitz grand cross of the house order of the wendish crown  january   netherlands knight grand cross of the order of the netherlands lion  march   oldenburg grand cross of the house and merit order of peter frederick louis  april   japan order of the rising sun grand cordon with paulownia flowers  september   baden grand cross of the house order of loyalty  may   spain order of the golden fleece  may   portugal knight grand cross of the order of christ  may   saxeweimareisenach knight of the house order of the white falcon  may   sweden knight of the royal order of the seraphim  may   grand duchy of hesse grand cross of the grand ducal ludwig order  may   kingdom of bavaria knight of the order of saint hubert  may   belgium grand cordon of the order of leopold  may   bulgaria grand cross of the order of st alexander  may   greece grand cross of the order of the redeemer  may   denmark knight of the order of the elephant  may   france grand cross of the legion of honour  may   holy see grand cross of the order of the holy sepulchre jerusalem patriarchate  may   hungary grand cross of the order of saint stephen of hungary  may   kingdom of italy order of the most holy annunciation  may   kingdom of italy knight grand cross of the order of saints maurice and lazarus  may   kingdom of italy knight gr